name: StaticBucketMapTest
description: Unit tests for StaticBucketMap class, focusing on key and value checks, including null handling.

test_cases.name: test_containsKey_nullMatchesIncorrectly
test_cases.description: Tests the containsKey method with null key, ensuring it matches correctly and does not incorrectly match other keys in the same bucket.

test_cases.name: test_containsValue_nullMatchesIncorrectly
test_cases.description: Tests the containsValue method with null value, ensuring it matches correctly and does not incorrectly match other values in the same bucket.

test_cases.name: test_get_nullMatchesIncorrectly
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with null key, ensuring it retrieves the correct value and does not incorrectly retrieve values for other keys in the same bucket.
